[0] https://pypi.python.org/pypi/mccabe

[1] Install: pip install mccabe

[2] This module provides a plugin for flake8, the Python code checker.

Example:
    python -m mccabe --min 5 example.py
Result:
    ("185:1: 'PathGraphingAstVisitor.visitIf'", 5)
    ("71:1: 'PathGraph.to_dot'", 5)
    ("245:1: 'McCabeChecker.run'", 5)
    ("283:1: 'main'", 7)
    ("203:1: 'PathGraphingAstVisitor.visitTryExcept'", 5)
    ("257:1: 'get_code_complexity'", 5)

